      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual transmission to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, maintaining the balanced handling characteristics of its MacPherson/multi-link suspension geometry. A mechanically sound example that balances raw performance with refined engineering, showing only minor cosmetic wear consistent with its enthusiast ownership.",
